{"title":"2025 Sea Otter Classic Day 01: Bikes and People – Spencer Harding and John Watson","link":"https://theradavist.com/sea-otter-classic-day-01/","date":1744369205000,"content":"<p><em>John and Spencer are walking the dusty aisles of Laguna Seca for the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/2025+Sea+Otter+Classic/\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Sea Otter Classic</a>. For the Sea Otter Classic Day 01 gallery, we focused on some of the amazing custom builds at the show. Don’t miss all the eye-popping details below…</em></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1-Up USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Prestons_Scarab-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Preston’s <a href=\"https://rotorbike.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rotor</a>-Equipped Drop Bar <a href=\"https://scarabcycles.com/pages/darien?\" target=\"_blank\">Scarab Darién</a></h3>\n<p>Preston, who works at Rotor Components, had his dream drop-bar MTB built by Colombia’s Scarab Cycles. It is fitted with a plethora of Rotor components, including their 1×13 hydraulic-actuated groupset. Painted in an homage to Utah and adorned with blooming globe mallow flowers, the bike is quite the looker.</p>\n<p>Check out <a href=\"https://rotorbike.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rotor</a> and <a href=\"https://scarabcycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Scarab</a> for more!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-17.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-17.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-17.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-17.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-1.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-1.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://madronecycles.com/collections/all\" target=\"_blank\">Madrone Jab Updates and 2.5 mm Offset UDH Hanger</a></h3>\n<p>When we saw Madrone’s assembled in the USA (from made in China parts) Jab derailleur pre-ordered opened up last year, we ordered one. While we eagerly await its delivery later this summer, Aaron had some new tidbits to show us. He’s improved upon the tooling for the derailleur repair module thanks to feedback from <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/madrone-cycling-axs-rebuild-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Spencer’s Tinker Tantrum</a>. He also had some current prototype derailleurs in long and short cages.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Madrone-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>But these 2.5 mm offset UDH hangers caught our eye. When John was building up a review bike, he ordered a silver Transmission cassette, only to find it was 2.5 mm wider than the standard Eagle cassette cluster and wouldn’t work on the UDH, non-T-type review bike. If he had this 2.5 mm UDH “standard” derailleur hanger, he could have been able to use the Transmission cassette and his non-SRAM cable-actuated derailleur. While it might feel like a specialty option for nerds (like us), it will allow Madrone customers to use one of the brand’s derailleurs with Transmission cassette clusters on UDH bikes. Phewwww.</p>\n<p>This clever design is why we love talking to smaller brands at Sea Otter.</p>\n<p>Follow along at <a href=\"https://madronecycles.com/collections/all\" target=\"_blank\">Madrone</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-8.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-8.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-8.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Prince-Cinelli-Vigorelli-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/prince.nrg/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Prince and His Cinelli Vigorelli</a></h3>\n<p>Hot damn. Dura Ace 7700 on a purple Cinelli Vigorelli? What is this? 2010? Prince was in attendance at Sea Otter today with drip for days. Yes, he was wearing that outfit in the blazing hot sun, too.</p>\n<p>Follow along at <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/prince.nrg/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Prince’s Instagram</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-13.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-13.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-11.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-11.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-11.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Omnium_Mini-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://omniumcargo.us/mini/\" target=\"_blank\">Omnium Mini </a></h3>\n<p>Sporting a shiny silver bling kit from <a href=\"https://velo-orange.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Velo Orange</a>, this little cargo bike is stylish and oh so cute. A gold chain, polished Velocity rims, and knobby Schwalbe complete the rig. Here’s to hoping for more silver bike parts this year.</p>\n<p>Check out the rest of the cargo hauling lineup at <a href=\"https://omniumcargo.us/\" target=\"_blank\">Omnium</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-ENVE-Mog-Spitfire-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=5872b9e2-f108-4d83-be91-e39d1275c1c1&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fenve.com%2Fcollections%2Fmog\" target=\"_blank\">Custom Flying Tigers Themed ENVE Mog Gravel Bike</a></h3>\n<p>The ENVE Mog is one of the nicest-looking carbon gravel bikes on the market. This custom-painted “shark mouth” insignia is inspired by the 1940s World War 2 First American Volunteer Group, also known as the Flying Tigers. This group painted the “shark mouth” design on its Curtiss P-40 Warhawks. While other planes also donned this iconic design, the Flying Tigers made it famous. Oh yeah… the bike looks so damn good, too!</p>\n<p>See the Mog at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=5872b9e2-f108-4d83-be91-e39d1275c1c1&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fenve.com%2Fcollections%2Fmog\" target=\"_blank\">ENVE</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Haro_Rivette-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://harobikes.com/products/rivette-carbon-ltd\">Haro Rivette Carbon LTD </a></h3>\n<p>Partnering with the UK-based illustrator and animator <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/markwardstudio/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Mark Ward</a> for the amazing custom artwork on this limited edition run of Haro’s performance road bike. Seeing such a high-end road bike from Haro with BMX-inspired artwork really brings the whole modern Haro lineup together.</p>\n<p>Check out more from <a href=\"https://harobikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Haro Bikes.</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Forbidden_Puritan-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://forbiddenbike.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Forbidden Bike Company Puritan \\m/</a></h3>\n<p>A pet project of the owner of Forbidden to make a shreddy commuter, BC style. This bike is just a prototype at the moment, but we’ll be keeping an eye if it comes to fruition. The Forbidden Puritan is probably the best and most metal bike name we’ve found so far. Blast beats and blackened vocals here we come!</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://forbiddenbike.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Forbidden</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Robs_VVA_Topanga-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Rob’s VVA Topanga</h3>\n<p>An avid collector of all things Victor Vicente of America, Rob was at the show with his Son riding another VVA. These are some of the earliest mountain bikes being built independently around the time Joe Breeze was making his first frames up in Marin. Victor Vicente of America – the original alt cyclist – is known to have eaten every North American mammal in the form of road kill. Yum! Yay for mini bikes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter_Telepathy-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.telepathybikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Telepathy Bikes</a></h3>\n<p>Telepathy’s intricate SYNC linkage is all in the name of balance to give the front and rear wheels a parallel wheel path. The whole bike is manufactured and built in Bozeman Montana. If a big hit DH bike doesn’t get you excited maybe the amazing glitter fleck paintjob will!</p>\n<p>Find out more at <a href=\"https://www.telepathybikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Telepathy Bikes.</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-6.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-6.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-5.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Luma-Starparty-5.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://lumacycles.com/products/starparty\" target=\"_blank\">Luma Cycles Starparty Gravel Bike</a></h3>\n<p>Jayme from Luma Cycles was displaying the brand’s Starparty gravel bike. This is the Philadelphia-based brand’s first Sea Otter. We think they nailed it with the Starparty bike’s landing at the show. These titanium frames feature a UDH, MRP Baxter fork, T47 bottom bracket, rack mounts, an off-road tuned geometry, and plentiful tire clearance.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://lumacycles.com/products/starparty\" target=\"_blank\">Luma Cycles</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-6.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-6.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-6.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025_Sea_Otter-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-11.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-11.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-21.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-21.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-21.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-21.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-29.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-29.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-29.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-49.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-49.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-49.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-49.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-24.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-24.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/04/2025-Sea-Otter-Show-24.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Sea Otter Day 01 Frenz and More!</h3>\n<p>Sea Otter isn’t just about bikes; it’s about connecting with friends and the people who make the bike industry so vibrant. Check out the Gallery for more photos of people, products, and more!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>The Radavist thanks <a href=\"https://1up-usa.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1-Up USA</a> for sponsoring our Sea Otter Classic coverage and our independent Reportage!</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/sea-otter-classic-day-01/\">2025 Sea Otter Classic Day 01: Bikes and People</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"db914dd3eba0d17c5e4208cb535